Course  
Requirements and Grades:

 


The course grade 
will be based on the following: 


1. out of class, 
open-book mid-term exam (20%); 


2. out of class, 
open-book final exam (20%); 


3. term paper 
report and presentation (40%); and


4. assigned 
homework and contribution to class discussions (20%). 
　




















































































































　



 
